Facebook

RADIO - Requirements, High Level Architecture, Data flow, Interface, Optimization/Performance

  Requirements - Functional and Non Functional
    Functional
      Must have
      - Post feed
      - Post support text, image and videos
      - Infinite scroll
      - Add, delete or edit post
      - Like or comment on post
      - Basic user profiles
      Nice to have
      - Search
      - Internationalization
    Non Functional
      - Performance
      - Mobile friendly
      - Accessibility
      - Offline support
